data.description: Wow! This house has so much to offer. The 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom split-level home is perfectly located on a double lot AND is positioned at a dead end providing lots of privacy and space. When you walk inside, be prepared to be surprised by the spacious rooms. Large kitchen and combined living and dining room is more space than you'll know what to do with. It also offers a  finished basement and attached 2-car garage. The only thing it needs is a little TLC. Come and check it out for yourself!
